" ctrl+p
" <C-W><C-v> open in vertical split
" <C-W><C-x> open in horizontal split

" <C-o> older jump position
" <C-i> newer jump position

" Increment / Decrement numbers
nnoremap <A-a> <C-a>
nnoremap <A-x> <C-x>

nnoremap ö {
nnoremap ä }

" replace and jump
nnoremap c* *Ncgn

" Yank from cursor to end of line
nnoremap Y y$

